  "_aboutme": [
    "ABOUTME: Curated filter-family taxonomy: family -> raw stat ids (devotions-parity",
    "ABOUTME: families over the deposit's key vocabulary; the pet family is source-based).",
    "Membership rules mirror web/src/core/statFormat.ts (Life=Vitality, Poison=Acid,",
    "offensiveSlow* DoTs fold into their damage family). Extending a family or adding one",
    "is a data change here, never a schema change. Drift guard: every id listed must exist",
    "in the deposit's key census; scripts/build_derived.py fails loudly otherwise.",
    "The pet family has no id list: membership is stats.source = 'pet_bonus'."
